main_body:
For products from the 1999/2000 marketing year, the storage aid provided for in Article 9(4) of Regulation (EC) No 2201/96 shall be:
(a) EUR 0,1767 per day and per tonne net weight until 28 February 2001 and EUR 0,1507 per day and per tonne net weight from 1 March 2001 for dried grapes;
(b) EUR 0,1728 per day and per tonne net weight for dried figs.
